OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FDuring the broadcast, presenter
OL,12,FStephen Dixon said the questions to be
OL,13,Fasked by undecided voters had not been
OL,14,Fseen in advance by the prime minister
OL,15,For by GB News.
OL,17,FGB News is currently being
OL,18,Finvestigated by Ofcom for a number of
OL,19,Fother shows, including many over
OL,20,Fimpartiality issues.
