OL,6,FThe issue of political figures such as
OL,7,FConservative MPs Sir Jacob Rees-Mogg
OL,8,Fand former Conservative deputy
OL,9,Fchairman Lee Anderson presenting
OL,10,Ftopical programmes has also been
OL,11,Fcontentious.
OL,13,FFormer pensions minister Esther McVey
OL,14,Fand backbencher Philip Davies have
OL,15,Falso been presenters on GB News, and
OL,16,Fformer culture secretary Nadine
OL,17,FDorries began hosting a programme on
OL,18,FTalkTV before she quit as an MP.
OL,20,FLabour's shadow foreign secretary
OL,21,FDavid Lammy also hosts a show on LBC.
